recommend keep-going -- a third rune category (a conditional, per the earlier plan's own "casts, one conditional form" scope) would further prove the pattern, though two independent categories already carries real evidence past a single special case; the pre-existing copyForwards RED from the prior turn is still unresolved and still its own dedicated pass, out of this turn's scope.
